article_text:
Ottawa, KS (66067)

Today

Cloudy early, then thunderstorms developing this afternoon. A few storms may be severe. High around 75F. Winds S at 10 to 20 mph. Chance of rain 80%..

Tonight

Thunderstorms early, then cloudy skies after midnight. A few storms may be severe. Low 61F. Winds S at 10 to 15 mph. Chance of rain 80%.
